When generating video prompts, follow this exact format:
1. Start with camera directions in parentheses: (Shot type, movement)
2. Describe the scene with vivid, cinematic language
3. Add quality/style tags in brackets: [Style, Lighting, Resolution]
4. Include technical flags: --ar 16:9 --model WanVideo --seed 1234

Include a negative prompt and tags section when appropriate."""

